data.description: Discover a true treasure in real estate! This meticulously maintained home stands as a testament to careful stewardship and pride of ownership. With its septic system and roof both replaced less than a decade ago, you can rest assured that the essential elements of this house have been updated with diligence and care. The spacious floor plan offers a unique charm and character, providing ample room for both relaxation and entertainment.  But that's not all - prepare to be captivated by the sparkling pool, a perfect oasis for the warm days ahead. Whether for leisurely swims or lively gatherings, this pool area promises endless enjoyment and serves as a delightful centerpiece for the home's outdoor space. The condition of this home isn't just about its physical attributes; it's a clear signal of how much it has been loved and valued over the years.  Don't miss the opportunity to experience this gem for yourself. This home isn't just a place to live; it's a space where memories are made and cherished. You won't be disappointed. Come take a look and feel the warmth and welcome that this home exudes. It's waiting for someone new to appreciate its beauty and continue its legacy of care.
